msgctxt "357252"
msgid "来たか"
msgstr "Did you come"

msgctxt "357396"
msgid "龍馬"
msgstr "Ryoma"

msgctxt "357540"
msgid "武市"
msgstr "Takeshi"

msgctxt "357684"
msgid "ここを覚えてるか"
msgstr "Do you remember here"

msgctxt "357828"
msgid "親っさんが死んだ場所だ"
msgstr "It ’s the place where my parents died."

msgctxt "357972"
msgid "忘れるわけがない"
msgstr "I can't forget"

msgctxt "358116"
msgid "この１年で土佐は変わった"
msgstr "Tosa has changed in the last year"

msgctxt "358260"
msgid "だがここだけはあの日のままだ"
msgstr "But only here is the same as that day"

msgctxt "358404"
msgid "俺がそうさせた"
msgstr "I made it so"

msgctxt "358548"
msgid "あの日親っさんはな"
msgstr "That day my parents"

msgctxt "358692"
msgid "俺ではなく"
msgstr "Not me"

msgctxt "358836"
msgid "龍馬"
msgstr "Ryoma"

msgctxt "358980"
msgid "お前に土佐勤王党を託すつもりだったんだ"
msgstr ""
"I was going to entrust you with the Tosakino\n"
"Party"

msgctxt "359124"
msgid "何？"
msgstr "what?"

msgctxt "359268"
msgid "気付いてなかったか"
msgstr "Didn't notice"

msgctxt "359412"
msgid ""
"お前はそういう奴だ\n"
"昔っから"
msgstr "You're that kind of guy for a long time"

msgctxt "359556"
msgid "人のために自分を投げ出せちまうくせに"
msgstr "Even though I can throw myself out for others"

msgctxt "359700"
msgid "手前のこととなるとサッパリだ"
msgstr "When it comes to the front, it's refreshing"

msgctxt "359844"
msgid "俺は"
msgstr "I am"

msgctxt "359988"
msgid "お前のそういう甘さが許せなかった"
msgstr "I couldn't forgive your sweetness"

msgctxt "360132"
msgid "そんなお前に土佐を託そうとした親っさんもな"
msgstr "Some parents tried to entrust Tosa to you"

msgctxt "360276"
msgid "お前は勤王党の盟主でいたいがために"
msgstr ""
"Because you want to be the leader of the\n"
"Qin Wang Party"

msgctxt "360420"
msgid "親っさんを殺したっていうのか"
msgstr "Did you kill your parents?"

msgctxt "360564"
msgid "前にも言ったはずだ"
msgstr "I should have said it before"

msgctxt "360708"
msgid "一介の郷士が土佐を……"
msgstr "A villager takes Tosa ..."

msgctxt "360852"
msgid ""
"ましてこの国を変えようと本気で想うなら\n"
"手段になどこだわっていられない"
msgstr ""
"Moreover, if you really want to change this\n"
"country, you can't stick to the means."

msgctxt "360996"
msgid "革命には血が必要なんだよ"
msgstr "The revolution needs blood"

msgctxt "361140"
msgid ""
"お前や親っさんのような甘いやり方じゃ\n"
"世の中は変わらないんだ"
msgstr ""
"The world doesn't change in a sweet way\n"
"like you and your parents"

msgctxt "361284"
msgid "だが親っさんの考えは変わらなかった"
msgstr "But my parents' thoughts did not change"

msgctxt "361428"
msgid "だから俺は"
msgstr "So I"

msgctxt "361572"
msgid "親っさんの意志を継ぐために"
msgstr "To inherit the will of parents"

msgctxt "361716"
msgid "親っさんを殺したんだ"
msgstr "I killed my parents"

msgctxt "361860"
msgid "意志を継ぐために殺すだと？"
msgstr "Do you kill to inherit your will?"

msgctxt "362004"
msgid "そんなバカな話があるか！！"
msgstr "Is there such a stupid story! !!"

msgctxt "362148"
msgid ""
"親っさんの意志は\n"
"土佐を変えろってことだ"
msgstr "Parents' will is to change Tosa"

msgctxt "362292"
msgid "だが親っさんはその手段にこだわり過ぎた"
msgstr ""
"But parents were too particular about the\n"
"means"

msgctxt "362436"
msgid "血を流さない方法に　な"
msgstr "How to keep blood out"

msgctxt "362580"
msgid "だから"
msgstr "So"

msgctxt "362724"
msgid "親っさんの意志を邪魔しているのは"
msgstr "What is disturbing the will of parents"

msgctxt "362868"
msgid ""
"他ならぬ親っさんの存在\n"
"そのものだったんだよ"
msgstr ""
"It was none other than the very existence\n"
"of a parent."

msgctxt "363012"
msgid ""
"親っさんの目的を果たすために\n"
"育てられてきた俺が"
msgstr "I was raised to fulfill my parents' purpose"

msgctxt "363156"
msgid "その障害を排除するのは"
msgstr "Eliminating that obstacle"

msgctxt "363300"
msgid "当然のことだろ？"
msgstr "Naturally?"

msgctxt "363444"
msgid "武市"
msgstr "Takeshi"

msgctxt "363588"
msgid "お前……"
msgstr "you……"

msgctxt "363732"
msgid ""
"こんなことを言っても\n"
"お前に理解されないのは分かってる"
msgstr ""
"I know you can't understand me even if I\n"
"say this"

msgctxt "363876"
msgid "お前は親っさんによく似ているからな"
msgstr "Because you look a lot like your parents"

msgctxt "364020"
msgid "芹沢鴨に親っさんの暗殺を依頼した時から"
msgstr ""
"From the time I asked Serizawa Kamo to assassinate\n"
"my parents"

msgctxt "364164"
msgid "俺はお前の名……"
msgstr "I'm your name ..."

msgctxt "364308"
msgid "坂本龍馬の名を騙るようになった"
msgstr "I came to deceive the name of Ryoma Sakamoto"

msgctxt "364452"
msgid "何故だかわかるか？"
msgstr "Do you know why?"

msgctxt "364596"
msgid "俺とお前……"
msgstr "Me and you ..."

msgctxt "364740"
msgid "どっちが正しいのか　ケリをつけるためさ"
msgstr "Which one is right?"

msgctxt "364884"
msgid "俺は俺の信念を貫き"
msgstr "I stick to my beliefs"

msgctxt "365028"
msgid "血で世界を変える道を行く"
msgstr "Going the way to change the world with blood"

msgctxt "365172"
msgid ""
"新選組にいれば\n"
"いずれ“もう一人の龍馬”の噂は耳に入るだろう"
msgstr ""
"If you are in the Shinsengumi, you will\n"
"hear rumors about \"another Ryoma\"."

msgctxt "365316"
msgid "お前なら何もしないわけはない"
msgstr "You can't do anything"

msgctxt "365460"
msgid "坂本龍馬の名は"
msgstr "The name of Ryoma Sakamoto is"

msgctxt "365604"
msgid "お前への挑戦状だったんだ"
msgstr "It was a challenge to you"

msgctxt "365748"
msgid "挑戦状だと？"
msgstr "Is it a challenge?"

msgctxt "365892"
msgid "坂本龍馬という人間は"
msgstr "A person named Ryoma Sakamoto"

msgctxt "366036"
msgid ""
"歴史を血で塗り替えた男として\n"
"語り継がれるか"
msgstr ""
"Will it be handed down as a man who repainted\n"
"history with blood?"

msgctxt "366180"
msgid "それとも"
msgstr "Or"

msgctxt "366324"
msgid ""
"吉田東洋と同じ道を歩んだ男として\n"
"語り継がれるか"
msgstr ""
"Will it be handed down as a man who has\n"
"followed the same path as Yoshida Toyo?"

msgctxt "366468"
msgid "俺とお前のこの１年は"
msgstr "This year for me and you"

msgctxt "366612"
msgid ""
"その決着をつけるための\n"
"時間だったということだ"
msgstr "It was time to settle that."

msgctxt "366756"
msgid "どちらにせよ"
msgstr "anyway"

msgctxt "366900"
msgid "坂本龍馬は歴史を変えた男として名を刻む"
msgstr ""
"Ryoma Sakamoto makes a name for himself\n"
"as a man who changed history"

msgctxt "367044"
msgid ""
"親っさんの遺志を継いだことに\n"
"変わりはないと思わないか？"
msgstr ""
"Don't you think it's the same as inheriting\n"
"the wishes of your parents?"

msgctxt "367188"
msgid "馬鹿なこと言ってんじゃねえ"
msgstr "Don't say stupid things"

msgctxt "367332"
msgid "そんな勝負に"
msgstr "In such a game"

msgctxt "367476"
msgid "どんな意味があるっていうんだ"
msgstr "What does that mean"

msgctxt "367620"
msgid ""
"俺にとっちゃ\n"
"それが何よりも重要だったんだ"
msgstr ""
"It was more important to me than anything\n"
"else"

msgctxt "367764"
msgid "その為ならどんな手も使った"
msgstr "I used any hand for that"

msgctxt "367908"
msgid "お前の動きは逐一報告させたよ"
msgstr "I let you report your movements one by one"

msgctxt "368052"
msgid "新選組の山崎"
msgstr "Shinsengumi Yamazaki"

msgctxt "368196"
msgid "それに"
msgstr "in addition"

msgctxt "368340"
msgid "宿屋の女を使ってな"
msgstr "Use the woman in the inn"

msgctxt "368484"
msgid "おりょうのことか"
msgstr "Do you mean Oryo?"

msgctxt "368628"
msgid "全て上手くいっていた"
msgstr "Everything went well"

msgctxt "368772"
msgid ""
"お前が薩長の仲を\n"
"取り持ったこともうまく利用して"
msgstr ""
"Make good use of your relationship with\n"
"Satsuma"

msgctxt "368916"
msgid ""
"この国に倒幕戦争を引き起こす寸前まで\n"
"持っていくこともできた"
msgstr ""
"I was able to bring this country to the\n"
"point of causing a defeat war"

msgctxt "369060"
msgid "だが"
msgstr "But"

msgctxt "369204"
msgid "大政奉還まで成し遂げちまうとはな"
msgstr "I don't want to achieve the Taisei Hokan"

msgctxt "369348"
msgid ""
"あれには\n"
"俺も奥の手を使わざるを得なかった"
msgstr "I had to use my back hand for that"

msgctxt "369492"
msgid "それで"
msgstr "So"

msgctxt "369636"
msgid "京へ火を"
msgstr "Fire to Kyo"

msgctxt "369780"
msgid "ああ"
msgstr "Oh"

msgctxt "369924"
msgid "だがそれすらお前は乗り越えやがった"
msgstr "But even that you got over it"

msgctxt "370068"
msgid "まさか本気の以蔵すら倒すとはな"
msgstr "No way to defeat even the serious Izo"

msgctxt "370212"
msgid "愛する女の裏切りさえ受け入れた"
msgstr ""
"I even accepted the betrayal of my beloved\n"
"woman"

msgctxt "370356"
msgid "どこまで行っても変わらねえよ　お前は"
msgstr "No matter how far you go, it doesn't change"

msgctxt "370500"
msgid "だからお前をここへ呼び出したのさ"
msgstr "That's why I called you here"

msgctxt "370644"
msgid "俺とお前"
msgstr "Me and you"

msgctxt "370788"
msgid "誰にも邪魔されず"
msgstr "Undisturbed by anyone"

msgctxt "370932"
msgid "最後の決着をつけるためにな"
msgstr "To make the final decision"

msgctxt "371076"
msgid "それで初めて……"
msgstr "Then for the first time ..."

msgctxt "371220"
msgid "俺は俺の正しさを証明できる"
msgstr "I can prove my correctness"

msgctxt "371364"
msgid "兄弟"
msgstr "brothers"

msgctxt "371508"
msgid "兄弟か"
msgstr "Brother"

msgctxt "371652"
msgid "懐かしい響きだ"
msgstr "It sounds nostalgic"

msgctxt "371796"
msgid "その言葉を聞くと"
msgstr "When you hear that word"

msgctxt "371940"
msgid "心の底から"
msgstr "From the bottom of my heart"

msgctxt "372084"
msgid "熱いものがこみ上げてくる"
msgstr "Hot things come up"

msgctxt "372228"
msgid "だが"
msgstr "But"

msgctxt "372372"
msgid "もう戻ることなどできない"
msgstr "I can't go back anymore"

msgctxt "372516"
msgid "坂本龍馬として生きた男は"
msgstr "The man who lived as Ryoma Sakamoto"

msgctxt "372660"
msgid "２人いらない"
msgstr "I don't need two people"
